Proposed caption: The C-LARA-2 page-by-page linguistic annotation editor.
Page-level layer controls select translation, MWE, lemma/POS, gloss and
romanisation. One segment is displayed with its translation and an editable
token table whose columns show token, MWE, lemma, POS and gloss; the page view
ends with an explicit per-segment save control.
